OL,3,CHow can 'fart chambers' help fight
OL,4,Cglobal warming?
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew visits a farm in Yorkshire where
OL,8,Fan unusual solution to reducing the
OL,9,FUK's carbon emissions is being trialled
OL,11,FAround 6% of the UK's greenhouse gas
OL,12,Femissions come from livestock.
OL,14,FMuch of that is methane - released
OL,15,Fwhen cows and sheep burp, belch, and
OL,16,Fyes, fart.
