OL,3,CHow can 'fart chambers' help fight
OL,4,Cglobal warming?
OL,6,FThe trials are taking place at Home
OL,7,FFarm in Swinithwaite, deep in the
OL,8,FYorkshire Dales, which is home to
OL,9,Fseveral breeds, including Swaledale
OL,10,Fsheep, named after a local valley.
OL,12,F"We're trying to establish if the
OL,13,FSwaledale sheep is the best sheep for
OL,14,Four native environment," the Farm's
OL,15,Fowner, Adrian Thornton-Berry, told me.
OL,17,F"We've got moorland, which is one of
OL,18,Fthe world's rarest resources and that
OL,19,Fneeds an animal to graze it.
