OL,3,CHow can 'fart chambers' help fight
OL,4,Cglobal warming?
OL,6,F"A lot of the local farmers are
OL,7,Fswitching more to a commercial breed,
OL,8,Fwhich isn't as well suited, I believe,
OL,9,Fto the natural habitat as a natural
OL,10,FSwaledale sheep."
OL,12,FBy comparing emissions from the hardy
OL,13,Fblack-faced Swaledale to Texel crosses
OL,14,F- a meatier, introduced breed -
OL,15,Fscientists hope to assess how well
OL,16,Feach digests the rugged hill pastures.
