OL,3,CHow can 'fart chambers' help fight
OL,4,Cglobal warming?
OL,6,F"The agricultural sector has committed
OL,7,Fto getting to net zero by 2040, so
OL,8,Freducing methane in our sheep and
OL,9,Fcattle will be part of achieving that."
OL,11,FIt will take months to collect and
OL,12,Fanalyse all the data.
OL,14,FBut Adrian hopes that giving Swaledale
OL,15,Fsheep an environmental value will help
OL,16,Fsecure their place in the Dales - and
OL,17,Fprotect the precious moorland they
OL,18,Fhelp to sustain.
